  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Defending the water rights of the Katari River Basin communities</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IIADI will work with communities affected by the contamination of the Katari River Basin in the La Paz department, Bolivia. Through a combination of investigation, training and advocacy, the project will support the generation and implementation of actions to combat the contamination at five key locations. The team will also work with a team of local youth environmental rights activists and promote the articulation between this group, the affected communities and other organisations and actors.</narrative>
  </description>
